DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages ssh
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include ssh              # Install and run ssh with standard configurations.
include ssh::disable     # Disable ssh service.
include ssh::disableboot # Disable ssh service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include ssh::absent      # Remove ssh package.

DEPENDENCIES:
